Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎蛋卷的邊切壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那塊待會給唯芳先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那裡我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯芳先生是想要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點不漏地品嚐小夜的煎蛋卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是您那麼喜歡煎蛋卷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜會更加努力精進的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三話「人心莫測」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎蛋卷很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會努力做得更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.39,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先喝咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜和唯芳先生的不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙只喝很淡的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說好吃 所以我又做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃這個的時候 好像人都輕飄飄的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為手感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 不單單是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是心情都變得輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和咖啡搭配起來 更加輕飄飄的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕飄飄的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯芳先生 那個要嘗嘗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和父親一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共進了早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味的Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大路很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊可能會有車子經過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為碰到小狗所以遲到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過讓我多了個幫忙收拾準備室的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣抵遲到懲罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這學校也就這麼清閒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我也樂得清閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒鳥老師 當老師之後一直在這學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當上老師以後的話 是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前不是幹這個的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是搞研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和現在教的科學略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辭了那個來做了老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前開始就好奇心很重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想知道什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不做這份工作就無法知曉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣你呢 在學校的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 有什麼很在意的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 大家有沒有什麼介意的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親總是說我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 說不定是相當沒常識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是給大家添麻煩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦沒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不都很喜歡更衣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要是有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找我商量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得下午沒課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒玩玩再回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鎮上有什麼可以選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優花欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣 還是想去哪裡玩玩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生會做的 好玩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家想做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾 寧寧 別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前說發現一家蛋糕好吃的店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得 我真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的就是Cafe Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪 咖啡廳之類的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就那一家 別無選擇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡為什麼是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂趣 樂趣在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被更衣拒絕 還真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倍兒有面子的帶她去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現是知道的店 甚至還是常客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟臉也得有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去Guimauve吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃蛋糕麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像高中生麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生做的真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她去Guimauve 這個可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學還真是超乎想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很舒服 但是太閒適了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是閒適 不如說是閒散
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你們再抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的景觀和人口密度也不會變啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這是個平靜的好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 太靜了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼靜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別想發生點什麼事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好有默契啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像說相聲的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少該說是像偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者組合什麼的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不看電視的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指不看搞笑 綜藝節目之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看 因為家裡沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 是說沒有電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是僅指房間裡沒有吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個神社和你家…都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過著沒有電視的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼不方便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在家幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神社幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有做作業和…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娛樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和父親聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有去Guimauve玩也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味的蛋糕和咖啡在等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 大家都來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不怎麼喜歡吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道是怎麼做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是會自己做蛋糕之類的那種人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種烹調我都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引小夜注意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小夜能明白我是在吸引她注意的話還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜這堵牆好高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是時真同學也一起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找他時 他已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 我是該鬱悶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是順其自然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾您營業了 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣 鶯商店的店主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前天就沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一說…剛才是關著的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒有聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他妻子說以前從來沒有這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來通知一下周圍的鄰居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你特地來告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們 趁天亮趕緊回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有出現在八卦中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 今夜必定出現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能和之前的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論它有多麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜都會把它擊敗 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爾要遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 既有變化之處又有不變之處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也無法改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最根本的那部分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那部分改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前還是同一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在那以前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂根本 是不變的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…即將揭曉…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真同學不吃便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.80,0:23:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其吃 還不如睡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 空著肚子會變得悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺氣氛不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的氣氛很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 不就能預見故事的發展了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不允許這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不能允許
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲歎吧